        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'But in Nanami\\'s imagination, such compromise should not be tolerated. That is why she returns this feeling to Constructs, so they can enjoy the same happiness as humans in the following traditional activities.'}"
